etomica.models.nitrogen

Class HarmonicAlphaNitrogenModelPairMoleculeSequential

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.simulation.Simulation
      • etomica.models.nitrogen.HarmonicAlphaNitrogenModelPairMoleculeSequential
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISimulation

    public class HarmonicAlphaNitrogenModelPairMoleculeSequential
extends Simulation
    This class is created to take care of Java out of memory problem when creating a 2D array that is gigantic [~10000][~10000] The class is write a 5 x (nA * dof) Matrix to file while looping through the molecules This class also applied the molecules pair identification algorithm to speed up the matrix construction.
